<h2></h2>
<h4><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">WhyÂ you should choose DTG:</span></h4>
<ul>
 	<li><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">Your garments are 100% cotton or high cotton blends.</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">Your graphic is a photograph or multi-color image with gradients.Â </span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">You would like your print on white garments to be as soft to the touch as possible.</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">You require a faster turnaround than standard screen printing would normally allow.</span></li>
